{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b76a1b191e","title":"尽快筹备进军西藏所需高空运输机","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3ab1140a24","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"5a9d41aaa9","index":1,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"b76a1b191e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"3047bb145e","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是毛泽东在中共中央西南局1950年8月20日关于攻占昌都的准备工作的报告上的批语。本篇二是毛泽东给李涛的信。李涛（1905-1970），湖南汝城人，当时任中国人民解放军总参谋部作战部部长。本篇三是毛泽东对李涛1950年8月24日关于筹组和购买高空运输机问题报告的批语。"},{"id":"1516545fb1","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央西南局1950年8月20日关于攻占昌都的准备工作给毛泽东的报告中的第七项。"},{"id":"984a668a3d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"94528a0b56","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"空司，即中国人民解放军空军司令部。"},{"id":"1aa393b4ea","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李涛的报告说：关于筹组三十架高空运输机以支援进军西藏的问题，经向空军司令部查询结果，最快亦须于一九五一年一月才可开始实现，上述时间还须保证向苏购买的飞机能于十一月到达才行。"}],"contents":[{"id":"54807c5123","type":"title","text":"尽快筹备进军西藏所需高空运输机”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"3047bb145e","type":"paragraph","text":"第七项请周以督促空司尽速筹备，并以情况告我。三十架飞机要是高空使用的，驾驶员亦须适合此项条件，请加注意为盼","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"1516545fb1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"984a668a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十三日李涛同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"94528a0b56","type":"paragraph","text":"西南军区为进军西藏，需要三十架高空运输机，请询空司是否已着手筹备，飞机和驾驶员何日可以筹妥，最近三四个月内有希望否，问明告我，并加督促为盼。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"1aa393b4ea","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"35369e7fff","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十三日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"1f6acf6fbe","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"c1e7a1b989","type":"paragraph","text":"周筹备，务于明年一月或二月或三月能有三十架（连现有九架）高空机。三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"04a29cf60a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"},{"id":"e3f37594c1","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十四日","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e"}],"page":{"id":"9c81d99062","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b76a1b191e","start":97,"end":98}}}},"__N_SSG":true}